{"tid":2236214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"雙十節舉青天白日滿地紅旗　消息指不違法","createTime":"2020-10-09T10:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T10:22:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae9bb16cf81dea0011f7aa1630acc7cd55b00ef","tid":2236214,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:06:16.000Z","msg":"明日(10日)為「雙十節」，有網民發起上街高舉青天白日滿地紅旗慶祝；亦有網民上載去年發起舉行「港台連線，雙十慶典」活動的海報。有消息指出，若有人只舉出青天白日滿地紅旗，並不會違法，警方要視乎當時的行為，包括有否其他人叫口號，以及有沒有煽動其他人作犯罪的行為。<br />\n<br />\n網民在社交媒體發起明日進行「10.10全民感謝日」行動，稱目的為振興本土經濟。另外，早前有團體計劃明日在酒樓慶祝「雙十節」，但疑因酒樓擔心觸犯《港區國安法》而拒絕酒席。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource: 東網"},{"pid":"afa8d90ef82dcd7af01cdce6ded0c30991ffc9e1","tid":2236214,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:06:44.000Z","msg":"洗撚你講咩。"},{"pid":"81024f6a0125c33cc89bc818acfe620f89845ac9","tid":2236214,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:07:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca470a45888ea246d1b8f0e9d7668799af6f6190","tid":2236214,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:08:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36ebaf42fd4c3f7dfefedee002848f89bdd9bce3","tid":2236214,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"點會拉香港班國民黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af59ad545ff07c08f43d30eb9f958a96b7872bc1","tid":2236214,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81024f6a0125c33cc89bc818acfe620f89845ac9","tid":2236214,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:07:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 